.TH APKW-CLI 1 "April 2026" "APKW" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
apkw-cli \- command line client for APK Workbench services
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B apkw-cli
\fICOMMAND\fR
[\fIARGS\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B apkw-cli
provides command line access to the APK Workbench job, workflow, project, toolchain,
target, observe, and build services.
.PP
Run
.B apkw-cli --help
or
.B apkw-cli \fICOMMAND\fR --help
to inspect the available subcommands and arguments.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/apkw/state/cli-config.json
Persisted CLI configuration.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR apkw (1),
.BR apkw-ui (1)
